title: Rich Nut and Fruit Cake
ingredients: ['4 eggs', '1/8 teaspoon salt', '1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract', '200g caster sugar', '200g plain flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '450g red glace cherries', '450g green glace cherries', '450g Brazil nuts', '450g walnut halves', '450g pecan halves', '900g pitted dates']
